Closing Statement

STINT-Money explores a fundamental idea:

Financial correctness can be preserved and reconstructed from structure—even without continuous network connectivity.

It is released openly to encourage:

independent validation
real-world testing
safe experimentation

STINT-Money is offered as a minimal reference implementation of tetherless structural settlement.
